  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a pan over medium heat. Add onions and cook until translucent.",
    "Add tomato paste, coriander seeds, fennel seeds, garam masala, and turmeric powder. Stir for about a minute to combine spices with the onion.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth. Bring it to boil then reduce heat to low and let simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Fold in green olives and chopped cilantro. Cook for an additional 5 minutes until ingredients are heated through and flavors have melded together.",
    "Serve warm as a side dish or on its own, drizzled with extra oil if desired."
